Russian for Root Companion

title: Change custom battery stats permission to normal & bump version to 1.6
message:
Change custom battery stats permission to normal & bump version to 1.6

This allows us to work better with the new Marshmallow permission model
by not requiring an explicit permission request.  The explicit request
works well when this is a known permission, but their model for custom
permissions is weak.  The fact that the user has installed the root
companion is good enough.

title: Ensure there is no way an entire directory is deleted on uninstall
message:
Ensure there is no way an entire directory is deleted on uninstall

Some users have reported that uninstall of the app wipes the entire
/system/priv-app directory.  In theory this could occur if the package
manager was returning empty values for locations (bug in the ROM
perhaps?).  This change set will do extra checks to ensure it only ever
deletes a single file.
